SUMMARY:Bingo night!
DESCRIPTION:Join us every other Wednesday at 6:30 PM for 5 exciting rounds of Bingo!  Bingo is free to play and family-friendly! We will have prizes from the Station Taphouse and the Station. The final round is extra special—it’s a community round\, where the prize will be items brought in by YOU!  So mark your calendars and bring your luck (and maybe a cool prize)!\n\n*Be sure to check the event host’s website in case the date is a holiday!*\n\nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/bingo-night/2026-03-25/
