SUMMARY:Spring Break Pop-Up Nature at Hoyt Arboretum
DESCRIPTION:When PPS and many Portland-area schools are out for spring break\, it also happens to be a wonderful time to explore nature at Hoyt Arboretum! \nEach day there will be an exploration station with an educator ready to share a new nature topic with you. \nHands-on activities and fun facts will help youth connect with the trees\, flowers\, and animals found throughout the Arboretum. Activities are designed for ages 3-8\, but all are welcome! \nDrop in at the Hoyt Arboretum Visitor Center to Participate. These events are free and do not require registration. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/spring-break-pop-up-nature-at-hoyt-arboretum/2026-03-26/
LOCATION:Hoyt Arboretum\, 4000 SW Fairview Blvd\, Portland\, OR\, 97221
