SUMMARY:OMSI React-O-Blast
DESCRIPTION:OMSI staff bring science to life with demos that let kids see\, hear\, and feel the wild world of matter in action – from reactions you can predict to surprises that pop and fizz. Audience participants experience what makes chemical reactions tick\, how physical and chemical changes differ\, and why safety is always part of the experiment. Designed especially for curious minds in grades K–8\, this program turns science into an adventure.
