DESCRIPTION:Parents\, we’ve got you. \nEvery day during spring break at 2pm\, we’re rolling a family favorite in the tasting room. Bring the kids\, grab a seat\, and enjoy a little afternoon break. \nMonday – Kung Fu Panda\nTuesday – Despicable Me\nWednesday – Sing\nThursday – The Incredibles\nFriday – Moana \nPopcorn for the kids. Wine for the parents. 🍿🍷\nSettle in and enjoy the show. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
